ETIQUETTE
Due to your years of experience in polite society, you know the importance of proper etiquette. When you converse with someone of rank or status, make a contested [DEX + INT] check. On a success, you leave them with a positive impression of you.

REFINED EDUCATION
After a lifetime of private study, you have memorized facts and trivia about much of the world. Whenever you see or hear something interesting, roll [INT + INT] with a TN set by the GM. On a success, you learn more detailed information about it.

TRAINED PRECISION
After extensive training on proper techniques, you can accurately and gracefully throw a Pokéball better than most. You receive +1 on your [DEX + INT] rolls to throw balls.
